{"tid":1259761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知所以會贏，因為信任","createTime":"2019-06-26T16:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T16:50:55.000Z","uid":208722,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"db47cc0d10357c72eb496e69f7eb9d0c02cbd1c3","tid":1259761,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:14:00.000Z","msg":"「香港人」唔係一個人，係一個想像嘅共同體<br />\n縱使每個「香港人」有唔同思考方式同手法，但「香港人」作為一個想像嘅共同體，仍然相信人會從良心行事，嚮往自由同法治社會，信任屬於自己群體的每個群眾<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n請相信前線香港人嘅判斷同毅力<br />\n請相信後方識得隨機應變同支援<br />\n<br />\n咁樣「香港人」先會贏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382add8d214ef3e6ed4c7efad2590963bae05036","tid":1259761,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}